article.headline: TCU 58, Houston 51
article.story: FORT WORTH, Texas (AP) -- Marcus Shropshire scored 14 points to lead TCU to a 58-51 victory over Houston on Wednesday night. Shropshire was 5-11 from the field for the Horned Frogs (13-5, 3-1 Conference USA). Femi Ibikunle had his second career double-double, scoring 12 points and grabbing 12 rebounds. Lanny Smith scored 24 points for Houston (11-7, 2-2), and was 9-of-20 from the field. He made six 3-pointers on nine attempts. Houston led at halftime 25-22.
